text: Dennis Martin Daugaard (pronounced DEW-guard; born June 11, 1953) is an American politician. He was the 32nd Governor of South Dakota from January 2011 to January 2019. ==Other websites== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:American Lutherans Category:Governors of South Dakota Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Lieutenant Governors of South Dakota
